p: CircRAB11FIP1 promoted autophagic flux. Therefore, the study explored whether circRAB11FIP1-induced autophagy participated in ovarian cancer cell proliferation and invasion. SKOV3 cells transfected with LV2-1 had decreased proliferation and invasion capacities. However, this effect was partly reversed after the ectopic expression of ATG5 and ATG7 (Fig. 3A–C). On the contrary, circRAB11FIP1 ectopic expression enhanced A2780 cell proliferation and invasion abilities. However, these effects were partly retarded after ATG5 or Beclin1 silencing (Fig. 3D–F).
